{"id": "ChIJedpuasfDwoAR64nBg4sq5aA", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 191, "displayName": {"text": "Oakobing", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJedpuasfDwoAR64nBg4sq5aA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWcmNFUmpWbXh0TFVneFEyRTBSblF6Y2t0WExVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I came with a friend to check this location out and I was pleasantly surprised: it's as good as the Koreatown location. The have a promo in which you get one large shaved ice (bingsu) with two drinks for just 26 dollars. It's totally worth it. Both drinks (Injeolmi Latte and Strawberry Milk) were great but the strawberry milk was better in my opinion. The whole place was quite busy and there was a line but we still got dispatched quickly and in a prompt manner.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I came with a friend to check this location out and I was pleasantly surprised: it's as good as the Koreatown location. The have a promo in which you get one large shaved ice (bingsu) with two drinks for just 26 dollars. It's totally worth it. Both drinks (Injeolmi Latte and Strawberry Milk) were great but the strawberry milk was better in my opinion. The whole place was quite busy and there was a line but we still got dispatched quickly and in a prompt manner.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "A.J. Foucault", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116880457762175011542/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1vF-EViYXoNRQPKg0GD2fd6G_hXaK99pVgixLUMfCp0clRks=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-05T21:23:23.697335571Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWcmNFUmpWbXh0TFVneFEyRTBSblF6Y2t0WExVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWcmNFUmpWbXh0TFVneFEyRTBSblF6Y2t0WExVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c76a6eda79:0xa0e52a8b83c189eb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJedpuasfDwoAR64nBg4sq5aA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poVFNtMHRaMkZyYWtSelJEWXdNV3BsUlhabGVVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Shaved ice was amazing. Selections are limited to what is on the menu but they don't miss. There is a flavor of the month as well so there's something new outside of those selections. It can get crowded quickly. The sweet milk isn't condensed milk but it was fun to pour over the shaved ice and eat.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Shaved ice was amazing. Selections are limited to what is on the menu but they don't miss. There is a flavor of the month as well so there's something new outside of those selections. It can get crowded quickly. The sweet milk isn't condensed milk but it was fun to pour over the shaved ice and eat.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lisa Runnel", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106992077266598489944/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWb_r_2-BKUlOJnAZ-d8Ku_QkXtoqjiQ3e4g4meKjAw3-jt6-2zw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-04T09:11:53.305401294Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poVFNtMHRaMkZyYWtSelJEWXdNV3BsUlhabGVVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poVFNtMHRaMkZyYWtSelJEWXdNV3BsUlhabGVVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c76a6eda79:0xa0e52a8b83c189eb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJedpuasfDwoAR64nBg4sq5aA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psbldWOVpjRjlOY0VwcFpVOU5MV2xGT0hGYU1tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Such a great spot! A tiny place, but we were driving through so we new we were taking ours to go.\n\nThis was a perfect end to our day, such yummy fruit and shaved ice. Can't wait to come back 😋", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Such a great spot! A tiny place, but we were driving through so we new we were taking ours to go.\n\nThis was a perfect end to our day, such yummy fruit and shaved ice. Can't wait to come back 😋", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Angel OP", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110162789749897659822/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOleJ6S_wXLMn-HOlfp5x-cmeiMoQkw2dm-9ermMym1gFQ3sI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-24T03:12:50.188063777Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psbldWOVpjRjlOY0VwcFpVOU5MV2xGT0hGYU1tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psbldWOVpjRjlOY0VwcFpVOU5MV2xGT0hGYU1tYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c76a6eda79:0xa0e52a8b83c189eb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJedpuasfDwoAR64nBg4sq5aA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psbU9HcFpWMWcyYUVOb01taElkelZ2VlhBNVYxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Delicious Korean shaved ice with fresh fruit!!  My go to is the mango melon.  They also have drinks, fresh fruits aside from shaved ice, but do get the shaved ice!! 5 stars 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟Very refreshing!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Delicious Korean shaved ice with fresh fruit!!  My go to is the mango melon.  They also have drinks, fresh fruits aside from shaved ice, but do get the shaved ice!! 5 stars 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟Very refreshing!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kat N.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104869090695460350807/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItU4ii4F4gn6LRjyzYVGcHtbSuL4Cu9_56rlsfHipLboMKJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-12T07:36:49.287575590Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psbU9HcFpWMWcyYUVOb01taElkelZ2VlhBNVYxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psbU9HcFpWMWcyYUVOb01taElkelZ2VlhBNVYxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c76a6eda79:0xa0e52a8b83c189eb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJedpuasfDwoAR64nBg4sq5aA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GamVEaG5PRVpLWkc1bVFWcDZXVzFRUmxJeU9IYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Oakobing always hits the spot when craving bingsu!  They have a variety of flavors and toppings to choose from and my favorites are the injeolmi and melon flavors.  It is a fun location to gather with friends and share dessert.  This location is on the smaller side, but most locations get busy regardless.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Oakobing always hits the spot when craving bingsu!  They have a variety of flavors and toppings to choose from and my favorites are the injeolmi and melon flavors.  It is a fun location to gather with friends and share dessert.  This location is on the smaller side, but most locations get busy regardless.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amanda Potchanatayparuk", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102629987364925365749/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjqDbKM0QcGIWR_oCvu_KKVxtnqVVS_AVFH1chLldi-EEH4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T22:10:26.910934442Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GamVEaG5PRVpLWkc1bVFWcDZXVzFRUmxJeU9IYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GamVEaG5PRVpLWkc1bVFWcDZXVzFRUmxJeU9IYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c76a6eda79:0xa0e52a8b83c189eb"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJedpuasfDwoAR64nBg4sq5aA/photos/AWCwydgoUADZsRGV--iOrmcvD19sHcoEid82djuCMgPJaWugbdi5AWFJCNK8vPvHi2E4CnHKzxpy_ELa4B6aIEWWWn_TZ9Cup